title: Pita Jungle - Dana Park
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of chain restaurant in the Southwest, offering Middle Eastern and Mediterranean food.
